QUICK INSTALLATION MANUAL FOR eyeOS
-----------------------------------

1) Download the latest version of eyeOS from http://www.eyeOS.org.

2) Uncompress the package to a local dir.

3) Upload the uncompressed eyeOS directory with your desired name.

4) Change read/write permissions to 777 of the following directories:

 etc/

5) Run index.php and complete installation (only one step).

Please, read the SECURITY MANUAL.

Enjoy eyeOS!
